<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head></head>
<body style="background-color:black;">
<div align="center" style="padding-top: 100px;">
<img align="center" alt="Todo Manager Logo" border="0" class="center autowidth" src="https://i.imgur.com/5vut1a3.png" style="border: 0; height: auto; width: 100%; max-width: 214px; display: block; title="Todo Manager Logo" width="214"/>
</div>
<div>
<div align="center" style="margin: 30px; min-height: 350px;" >
<p style="color:white; font-size: 36px;">Hi <%= @user.name %></p>
<p style="color:white; font-size: 16px;">We hope you have been well. This is a kind reminder that your following tasks are expiring soon:</p>
<table style="text-align: center; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; border-collapse: collapse; border: 3px solid #ddd; width: 100%;">
	<tbody>
	<tr>
	<th style="padding-top: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; text-align: center; background-color: #000; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; max-width: 100px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;">Task Name</th>
	<th style="padding-top: 12px; padding-bottom: 12px; text-align: center; background-color: #000; color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; max-width: 100px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;">Days Left</th>
	<% @expiringtasks.each do |key,value| %>
		<tr style="background-color: #f2f2f2;" key={id}>
			<td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px; max-width: 100px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;"><%= key %></td>
			<td style="border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px; max-width: 100px; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;"><%= value %></td>
		</tr>
	<% end %> 
	</tbody>
</table>
<p style="color:white; font-size: 16px;">If you do not wish to receive reminders for your tasks, you may turn off the notifications from your <a href="https://todo-manager.tjtanjin.com/profile">profile</a>.</p>
</div>
<footer style="background-color: white; height: 120px; text-align: center; padding-top: 20px">
<a href="https://github.com/tjtanjin/CVWO-assignment" target="_blank"><img alt="Github Logo" height="32" class="center autowidth" src="https://i.imgur.com/6JjO3tc.png" style="height: auto; border: none; display: block; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; title="Github Logo" width="32"/></a>
<p style="color: #808080; font-size: 14px;">Â© Todo Manager Copyright 2020</p>
</footer>
</body>
</html>